daily_routine: Wakes at 4am to check her father's old acoustic monitoring equipment
  for vaquita clicks that haven't been heard in three years. Repairs gillnets she
  knows kill what she loves most. Teaches her granddaughter traditional fishing songs
  while knowing there will be no fish left to sing to.
